---
permalink: /sitemap.xml
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
# Core pages listed explicitly (update lastmod when a page meaningfully
# changes). Blog posts are appended automatically from the posts collection
# so a new post can never be forgotten.
corePages:
  - url: /
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
  - url: /startups/
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
  - url: /waitlist/
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
  - url: /changelog/
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
  - url: /privacy/
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
  - url: /terms/
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
  - url: /learn/
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
  - url: /vision/
    lastmod: "2026-06-28"
---
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<urlset xmlns="http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9">
{%- for p in corePages %}
  <url><loc>https://gethouston.ai{{ p.url }}</loc><lastmod>{{ p.lastmod }}</lastmod></url>
{%- endfor %}
{%- set newest = collections.posts | reverse | first %}
{%- if newest %}
  <url><loc>https://gethouston.ai/blog/</loc><lastmod>{{ newest.date | isoDateOnly }}</lastmod></url>
{%- endif %}
{%- for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
  <url><loc>https://gethouston.ai{{ post.url }}</loc><lastmod>{{ post.date | isoDateOnly }}</lastmod></url>
{%- endfor %}
</urlset>
